snippet.title: Tiger Woods PGA TOUR® 13 | Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
EA SPORTS presents Tiger Woods PGA Tour 13. Tiger Woods PGA TOUR 13 is back and ready for another season of PGA TOUR golf.

Take on many of the world's top professional golfers as you work your way to #1 in the world.

Tiger Woods PGA TOUR 13 will be available for Xbox 360, PlayStation 3, and Nintendo Wii in 2012.
